---
title: "Professional Experience"
layout: "layout.njk"
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-12">
    <div class="mb-16 text-center">
        <h1 class="page-title mb-6">Professional Journey</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            A comprehensive history of my career in network engineering, technical support, and the early roles that shaped my work ethic.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative space-y-12 before:absolute before:inset-0 before:ml-5 before:-translate-x-px md:before:mx-auto md:before:translate-x-0 before:h-full before:w-0.5 before:bg-gradient-to-b before:from-blue-500/0 before:via-blue-500/50 before:to-blue-500/0">
        
        {%- for role in roles -%}
        <!-- Experience Item -->
        <div class="relative flex items-center justify-between md:justify-normal md:odd:flex-row-reverse group">
            <!-- Icon -->
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-blue-500/50 bg-brand-dark text-blue-400 shadow shrink-0 md:order-1 md:group-odd:-translate-x-1/2 md:group-even:translate-x-1/2 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:bg-blue-500 group-hover:text-white">
                <i class="fa-solid {% if role.featured %}fa-briefcase{% else %}fa-history{% endif %}"></i>
            </div>
            <!-- Card -->
            <div class="w-[calc(100%-4rem)] md:w-[45%] card p-6 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-all border border-transparent">
                <div class="mb-2">
                    <div class="font-bold text-white text-xl leading-tight">{{ role.title }}</div>
                    <time class="font-mono text-sm text-blue-400 block mt-1">{{ role.time }}</time>
                </div>
                {%- if role.company -%}
                <div class="text-blue-300 font-semibold mb-4 flex items-center">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-building text-xs mr-2 opacity-70"></i> {{ role.company }}
                </div>
                {%- endif -%}
                {%- if role.description -%}
                <div class="text-gray-400 text-base leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-line">{{ role.description }}</div>
                {%- endif -%}
            </div>
        </div>
        {%- endfor -%}

    </div>

    <div class="mt-24 p-8 glass-card rounded-3xl text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Want to see my full resume?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">You can download a PDF version of my resume for your records.</p>
        <a href="/resume" class="btn">Download Resume (PDF)</a>
    </div>
</div>
